{"tid":517512,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[An/IOS] 天命6（4）pvp是坑","createTime":"2018-01-02T11:26:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T11:49:39.000Z","uid":14638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"557f4d9538b5303351b513c3c1b065c147f7ce5d","tid":517512,"uid":14638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T11:26:34.000Z","msg":"天命6<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/104820_68141bce103654e5e4bf71a3e635ee49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F104820_68141bce103654e5e4bf71a3e635ee49.jpg&h=0d231a7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/104844_b37543addbdcfb04fd92131163f1913e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F104844_b37543addbdcfb04fd92131163f1913e.jpg&h=e7201f80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/104853_9e8ea78c5ef52e58df478de1f93176ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F104853_9e8ea78c5ef52e58df478de1f93176ec.jpg&h=1d3f550b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/21/125720_31a3d6730a6198361fd7f6c36dc1b8b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2F125720_31a3d6730a6198361fd7f6c36dc1b8b3.jpg&h=d5f7853a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nios: <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/tw/app/id1056040054?at=1010l3Vj&amp;ct=GNN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Ftw%2Fapp%2Fid1056040054%3Fat%3D1010l3Vj%26ct%3DGNN&d=MpJNZB9Gooef3DL4O5ImK%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=7a0a13f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/tw/app/id1056040054?at=1010l3Vj&amp;ct=GNN</a><br />\nandroid: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.netmarble.destiny\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.netmarble.destiny&d=MpJNZB9Gooef3DL4O5ImK%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=aee2ae9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.netmarble.destiny</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">本GAME首抽要打完第1章9關 送3千500石俾你10連1次</span><br />\n建議新手唔好太執著於有幾隻5星先開波 因為個機率無你想像中咁高 你刷到有幾隻靚5星 2046都黎緊 隻GAME送石有別於其他台伏GAME 佢送石可以用倒水黎形容 你遲開一日就拎少一日野 自己諗<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有1隻推薦5星加1隻推薦4星已經開得</span></span><br />\n首抽角色參考 不能盡信<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1ehIOZr-7koPmYrK0cHsmHEAF3pap4Tz2BQe2CvVf6hY/htmlview?usp=sharing&amp;sle=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1ehIOZr-7koPmYrK0cHsmHEAF3pap4Tz2BQe2CvVf6hY%2Fhtmlview%3Fusp%3Dsharing%26sle%3Dtrue&d=MpJNZB9Gooef3DL4O5ImK%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=22e8a505\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1ehIOZr-7koPmYrK0cHsmHEAF3pap4Tz2BQe2CvVf6hY/htmlview?usp=sharing&amp;sle=true</a><br />\n必開五星<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">拳</span>朱利安(MK) PVE推薦 高攻擊力 首隻可刷技5星英雄<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">剪</span>小林(雙爪) BREAK技破BUFF 主動技增加傷害效果 大大力沒有之一<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">剪</span>娜塔沙 攻補合一身 現時機率up英雄 最緊要夠淫<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">包</span>阿多尼斯(神坦) 高防無敵盾BREAK技 神坦沒有之一<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">包</span>芙蘭索娃(封面) 靚唔靚見人見志 大量BUFF配合下於PVP極強勢<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">包</span>克魯(藍熊) pvp萬惡break技暈人英雄 厚血<br />\n唔錯五星<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">拳</span>奧洛特加(黑肉) PVE推薦英雄 雙範圍技<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">拳</span>娜塔沙 全攻型淫娃 出血技能唔錯<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">剪</span>奧斯卡(米奇) 高爆擊異常狀態break技<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">剪</span>夏勒洛特(掃把) 加速cd完成 5星補<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">包</span>奧洛特加(黑肉) 範圍技攻BUFF PVE推薦英雄<br />\n另外有啲4星都唔錯 你首抽有1隻5星加呢啲4星都可以開<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">包</span>伊芙 4星神補<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">包</span>西阿拉 萬惡反射盾 pvp熱門英雄<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">包</span>索浩 4星神補 可刷技<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">剪</span>伊芙 4星無敵盾<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">剪</span>庫洛諾 4星加速cd英雄<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">剪</span>吉柏特 雙break技pvp英雄 高機率停止對方活動<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">預想情況</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/105840_3b096d5a19afe61cafa7e48dd7790b80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F105840_3b096d5a19afe61cafa7e48dd7790b80.jpg&h=32f12839&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">實際情況</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/110054_610c459e7ac2ba0928dcbae28e1015ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F110054_610c459e7ac2ba0928dcbae28e1015ea.jpg&h=8df25168&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每隻角色都會有兩個版本 <span style=\"color: blue;\">包</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">剪</span><span style=\"color: red;\">拳</span>其二 呢度講唔晒咁多 自己參考下個EXCEL同望下角色D技黎決定 點配隊無絕對<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">藍傘鎮POST</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/104917_ac2ec373013451d9d3b97500c936cc75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F104917_ac2ec373013451d9d3b97500c936cc75.jpg&h=f9b1869c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/110634_850839fbaca5322f93a8d4ab96baa4c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F110634_850839fbaca5322f93a8d4ab96baa4c1.jpg&h=ad722094&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a583d51d669d002b6f4a9cf95acd5f1dab952e3","tid":517512,"uid":14638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T11:27:30.000Z","msg":"開左GAME未輸過嘅話唔該輸返次 送1隻4星<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/110923_bdddfbc330a192631d3dabe848fc4a0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F110923_bdddfbc330a192631d3dabe848fc4a0a.jpg&h=44a425ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">新手會問：</span>我有咩咩5星 又有咩咩4星 應該點組隊呀<br />\n答：無絕對嘅組隊方法 當你首抽有1隻5星 普通難度你係尻auto嘅 去到困難 就多數一補 一坦 一打手 衝鋒可以自己衡量放唔同卡 因為唔知你係幾多補幾多打手 你夠補咪落隻攻衝鋒 冇break手咪放隻break做衝鋒<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">新手又會問：</span>隊長放邊隻呢<br />\n答：其實望下張卡個隊長技好易明嘅 有分勢力形式 有分包/拳/剪形式 亦有分全角色形 理解下招技 再望下自己書包有咩卡再執 其實好易嘅<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">新手又會再問：</span>咁如果我有多角色點搞<br />\n答：有特別pvp關係要相同角色名但唔同屬性先可以入場 如果係<span style=\"color: red;\">同名同屬</span> 你可以食左佢升技 或者留返係書包打飛機<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/21/123359_6d05ffe68438f3012cedcb418c971f23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2F123359_6d05ffe68438f3012cedcb418c971f23.jpg&h=b60daf98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">角色技能:</span></span><br />\n攻擊技 <span style=\"color: gold;\">金色ICON</span><br />\n補技/BUFF技 <span style=\"color: blue;\">藍色ICON</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/110558_04751162787404dd0630abce6c46ce56.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F110558_04751162787404dd0630abce6c46ce56.png&h=12b0c41d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n突破技 <span style=\"color: red;\">紅色ICON</span> 唔同BOSS有唔同BREAK POINT 想知係幾多 你望下BOSS條血下面啲黃色格仔 1為1格 3格咪3囉<br />\n至於隻角色嘅BREAK技 左上角有1/2嘅 1咪1 2咪2囉<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/110559_e01423190e3b51f471a2042a398322c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F110559_e01423190e3b51f471a2042a398322c9.jpg&h=2bc6b710&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點先BREAK到呢 BOSS有2點BREAK POINT 你隻BREAK技係1 就要打2次先BREAK到 BREAK成功就會破防 BOSS任你魚肉一段時間 你係破防狀態下打幾多HIT打幾多傷害會有一個分計俾你嘅 某D關係要你呢個分達到咁GREADE以上 自己試多幾次就會明白<br />\n衡鋒技 3隻色都有 視乎隻角色SETTING 好似都係主動技第2招<br />\n上面有提過可以食自己升技 1升2要1隻 2升3要2隻 如此類推 技能最高5lv 除左食自己外 競技場同公會都可以用相關點數去買技能拉君黎升技<br />\n隻GAME嘅數據其實做得好分明 有BUFF同無BUFF 同時 有相剋效果下真係兩個世界 你PVP打一次就會明白<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/21/123356_26e02daea834f288b837394ff025e617.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2F123356_26e02daea834f288b837394ff025e617.jpg&h=c838fbe8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">升星 強化 覺醒</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">MAX所需EXP:</span><br />\n3星MAX=1星+2星強化兔各1<br />\n4星MAX=2星+3星強化兔各1<br />\n5,6星角自己執啦我計唔掂<br />\nEXP關其實唔難打 搵隻補加2隻打手 小心D 睇住黎放<span style=\"color: red;\">BREAK技</span> D兔仔只係一舊肉 1日只可以打5場 跌5星兔機率唔算高 我打惡夢級平均只會跌2隻4星強化兔俾我<br />\n個人建議每RE一次關 只需<span style=\"color: red;\">100石</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">升星所需素材:</span><br />\n1星升2星=1星MAX+1星<br />\n2星升3星=2星MAX+2隻2星<br />\n3星升4星=3星MAX+3隻3星<br />\n4星升5星=4星MAX+4隻4星<br />\n5星升6星=5星MAX+5隻5星<br />\n素材兔只可抽不可打 每日可以抽1定2次 視乎你日任及其他任務完成度會送 不過素材兔個機率真係低到仆街 我1~4星素材兔券未撚中過4星兔 而食用方面要注意 素材兔唔SUPPORT異族性交易 <span style=\"color: red;\">拳頭</span>只可以食<span style=\"color: red;\">拳頭</span> <span style=\"color: orange;\">剪</span>係食唔到<span style=\"color: blue;\">包</span>的<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/110800_79ed1032a6252f217d5e8180304ffbc7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F110800_79ed1032a6252f217d5e8180304ffbc7.jpg&h=bf853bf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/110801_7426c78c8bbc785e953630aaf506d4cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F110801_7426c78c8bbc785e953630aaf506d4cf.jpg&h=74899375&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外你打普通關即一般副本 係會跌砌圖 <span style=\"color: red;\">20張砌圖</span>可以開一次降臨副本 副本對應3~4星角 砌圖有分<span style=\"color: red;\">唔同勢力</span> 開嘅都係相對勢力嘅角色降臨副本 通關會跌<span style=\"color: red;\">角色碎片</span> 儲夠碎片可以召喚角色<br />\n30張碎片=3星 50張碎片=4星 100張碎片=5星<br />\n降臨副本係隨機開 即係相同勢力嘅砌圖 有機會開出相對勢力嘅3星或者4星 朋友開嘅降臨副本你都可以打 限時1個鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/21/123353_97def8568c697d9a4ccba14e46a1e5b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2F123353_97def8568c697d9a4ccba14e46a1e5b5.jpg&h=0bb43db7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n升6星係一個大工程 建議唔好為左升1隻6星而亂尻咁食4星上5星 隻GAME個機率無你想像中咁高 10連只係保底一隻4星 當然如果你歐洲開一個10連出足10隻4星嘅話我一定建議你尻食佢老母嘅"},{"pid":"b29279ff3ff2b27304121692572eb43ba3dc869c","tid":517512,"uid":14638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T11:27:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\">覺醒</span><br />\n覺醒石係可以合成升1級嘅<br />\n低去中20-&gt;1 中去高10-&gt;1 高去最高5-&gt;1 最高去傳說50-&gt;1<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/21/124640_0ab3dfa842112109612e42c4b0305954.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2F124640_0ab3dfa842112109612e42c4b0305954.jpg&h=6829ccda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咩星要幾多石覺醒1次自己入角色覺醒頁睇 每覺醒1次 角色數據會有變動 覺醒3次就會俾套新衫你換<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/21/124639_0d216bb418f1051e4b77b0a99cf57593.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2F124639_0d216bb418f1051e4b77b0a99cf57593.jpg&h=0ec83e02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n覺醒關同EXP關1樣 <span style=\"color: red;\">建議每日用100石RE1次</span> 最好打你應付到嘅最高個關 因為出高階覺醒石機率好低 打法一樣 1補2打手或者1補一盾1打手 視乎你有乜而定 要注意嘅係 BREAK技係必需 因為困難打後嘅關 D怪好厚血厚防 你唔破防要打好耐<br />\n以下內容由KELLY提供<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">限時商鋪</span> 有5格要開 建議開晒<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/21/125722_5356bec0a516673c7364b3c5d7073000.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2F125722_5356bec0a516673c7364b3c5d7073000.jpg&h=0592e41d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n限時商店除左買覺醒石之外 仲可以買有%既紋章 同埋角色碎片<br />\n3星一塊=1200 30塊=36000<br />\n4星一塊=7000 50塊=350000<br />\n5星一塊=35000 100塊=3500000<br />\n每日任務大約20～30萬 即係2日既錢就買到隻4星 哩d儲下儲下就有<br />\n我買野係 <span style=\"color: red;\">%紋章&gt;覺醒石&gt;碎片</span><br />\n肯定唔會買既野 <span style=\"color: red;\">寶珠</span><br />\n順帶一提<br />\n5星進化君=75萬<br />\n技能君=100萬<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">寶珠強化：</span><br />\n1星=冇用(打後有錢先用黎解+15個石任)<br />\n2星=過渡+6就夠用 唔一定要刷到有%項先用 有錢可以+9<br />\n3星/4星<br />\n開始有追加能力 追加項冇得強化 冇得改變(即圖中防禦+2%個欄)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/150537_1ee0549043a436d9267e89de0d0103c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F150537_1ee0549043a436d9267e89de0d0103c2.jpg&h=a270d967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3星最高起始<span style=\"color: red;\">9.5%</span><br />\n每3/6/9/12/15會有一個額外強化效果 MAX時電腦會隨機5選4個幫你釘死係竇石上面<br />\n強化每級+0.3% 即係加0.9%/1.8%/2.7%/3.6%/4.5%<br />\n以下係一張3星同4星既圖(+15由唔提老母提供)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/151305_0dd2153904f779bdccc29094c72c86f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F151305_0dd2153904f779bdccc29094c72c86f3.jpg&h=f43e4aa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/151317_f5509ae9520e20cfc430c119d8046b3b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F151317_f5509ae9520e20cfc430c119d8046b3b.jpg&h=d6f2822f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可以計到佢粒4星起始係10.5%<br />\n而我粒3星起始係9.5%<br />\n小弟想表達既係如果你粒9.5% 3星一開始追加能力係+2%防禦力(圖1)<br />\n咁你粒3星就會&gt;4星<br />\n所以小弟建議平民刷3星會比較效率 因為強化好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每日入GAME後請大叫一聲左仔世界第一</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/21/123358_3031d856f30af030027862d4fae0a5c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2F123358_3031d856f30af030027862d4fae0a5c7.jpg&h=2fdf77b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開POST TEMPLATE<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/17ywvi2Id0FBJOksKwbfJxB6H_sz7njXU22LgMpX5NoY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F17ywvi2Id0FBJOksKwbfJxB6H_sz7njXU22LgMpX5NoY&d=MpJNZB9Gooef3DL4O5ImK%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=bbe8fcf5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/17ywvi2Id0FBJOksKwbfJxB6H_sz7njXU22LgMpX5NoY</a>"},{"pid":"cd2d5980179da9c72e2bd5b4b771e7505ae0fab8","tid":517512,"uid":36566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T11:49:39.000Z","msg":"推邊個好<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}